name: Lil' Bird of Doom
description:
Lil' Bird of Doom, 2006
Colored pencil and pencil on paper
Approximately 9.4″ x 7″, framed (12.5″ x 10.2″ size of frame)

This drawing is the original sketch of the painting which is known as the meme "Welcome to Most" or "Winged Doom.

The purchase of this NFT comes with the original framed drawing (international shipping included).

This NFT and the original drawing belong together and can only be purchased and/or sold together.
